<Content>Good place to stay. I am actually still staying here, and I can tell you that since the latest reviews on THIS site, they have changed a lot. New beds (VERY comfortable), high speed internet, recliner, DVD player, CD player, fitness center, and pretty big closet space for a hotel.My only negative comment is : The shower pressure is... odd. It's high enough to be comfy, but I think I'm just picky about my shower. Hot water!Very quiet! In a good location. 
