<Author>A TripAdvisor Member
<Content>Wonderful! Serves the purpose perfectly Wonderful experience! Serves the purpose extremely well! Rooms are spacious, amenities are great. Has a lovely kitchenette in case you plan to make or bring in food into the room. Service is prompt and courteous, has a pretty cool fitness center and a Convenience Center that works in the Honor System. Free Video rentals are available at the front desk. Laundry facilities are good, business center albeit small is sufficient. Location by the Galleria is awesome! Has a neat little barbeque place by the side.The only thing the hotel lacks is a spacious decorated lobby that the 5 star hotels boast of; but do you really care?It was great value for my 40 bucks! 
